---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Apply for the Accelerator">
  <Navigation />
  <main>
    <section class="apply-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>accelerator</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">The world's first all-female, all-technical accelerator.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="apply-intro-text">
      <p>The Tech Bros Accelerator is the world's first all-female, all-technical accelerator programme, built to support founding teams at an early stage & to propel them into investor-ready startups. It's an 8 week programme with a strong emphasis on customer discovery and product development, with an intense focus on building.</p>
      <p>The programme is open to applicants worldwide and takes place during the summer every year. It kicks off with a two-week hacker house in a cabin in the Norwegian mountains & is followed by a six-week hybrid programme, anchored in London, combining in-person collaboration with remote flexibility.</p>
      <p>The selection process is highly competitive, with an acceptance rate of 8.7%. We select the boldest, most ambitious candidates with a proven ability to build technical products and iterate quickly. You can find out more about our interview style <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/milettegillow_how-we-picked-the-tech-bros-cohort-1-from-activity-7350135114208534529-Tf47/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">here</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="apply-section" id="apply">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="manifesto-content">
          <h2>who you are</h2>
          <p>This programme is for women with STEM backgrounds who want to build something big.</p>
          <p>You're ambitious. You think deeply. You care about how things actually work. You want to learn from people who respect your intelligence and challenge you properly.</p>
          <p>You don't need hand-holding.<br />You need the right room.</p>

          <h2>what you get</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Two weeks in a hacker house in Norway, shoulder-to-shoulder with other exceptional builders.</li>
            <li>Six weeks of hybrid support, with weekly sessions and check-ins.</li>
            <li>Access to a venture partner network made up of founders and investors who back serious technical ambition.</li>
            <li>A demo day designed to lead to real investment.</li>
            <li>A cohort that becomes part of your professional life long after the programme ends.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>what we're here for</h2>
          <p>We're not here to inspire you.<br />We're here to back you.</p>
          <p>If you're ready to build something real, this programme is for you.</p>
        </div>


        <div class="apply-content">
          <div class="cohort-stats">
            <h2>cohort 1 by numbers</h2>
            <div class="stats-mini">
              <div class="stat-mini">
                <div class="stat-number">15</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Companies Accepted</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-mini">
                <div class="stat-number">8.7%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Acceptance Rate</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-mini">
                <div class="stat-number">9</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Countries Represented</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-mini">
                <div class="stat-number">10%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Y-Combinator Alumni</div>
              </div>
                <div class="stat-mini">
                <div class="stat-number">30%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Have a Ph.D.</div>
              </div>
                <div class="stat-mini">
                <div class="stat-number">65%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Attended top 20 university in the world</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-mini">
                <div class="stat-number">85%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">engineering, computer science, or AI background</div>
              </div>
              <div class="stat-mini">
                <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">STEM background</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-image-section">
        <img 
          src="/apply/cohort-hero.jpg" 
          alt="Cohort 1" 
          class="hero-image"
          fetchpriority="high"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
          width="1920"
          height="1080"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <div class="spotlight">
          <div class="spotlight-image">
            <img src="/apply/neurotype-spotlight.jpg" alt="Neurotype" />
          </div>
          <div class="spotlight-content">
            <h2>spotlight: neurotype.uk</h2>
            <p>Building AI-powered tools to eliminate waiting lists for neurodiversity assessment professionals. Founded by a senior clinical psychologist with a Ph.D. in neuroscience from Oxford and ML engineer with deep domain expertise in AI for medical applications. They entered the programme with an early-stage concept and left with an MVP, and have since launched 4 pilots, secured 8 Letters of Intent, received Innovate UK funding (which has a less than 2% success rate); they now have a pipeline worth over £20 million.</p>
            <a href="https://neurotype.uk" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="apply-intro">
          <p class="section-intro">Applications for cohort 2 open in March 2026.</p>
          <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
            <a href="/apply/join-community" class="btn btn-secondary">Join Community</a>
            <a href="/apply/faq" class="btn btn-secondary">Read FAQ</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .apply-hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .apply-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .manifesto-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .manifesto-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .manifesto-content h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .manifesto-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .manifesto-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .manifesto-content ul li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .manifesto-content ul li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .apply-intro-text {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .apply-intro-text p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .apply-intro-text a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .apply-intro-text a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .apply-intro {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 4rem auto 0;
  }

  .apply-intro .btn-secondary {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(239, 31, 159, 0.3);
  }

  .apply-intro .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-bg-end);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(239, 31, 159, 0.5);
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .apply-content {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .cohort-stats h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-image-section {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .stats-mini {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-mini {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(239, 31, 159, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .spotlight {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .spotlight-image {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .spotlight-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .spotlight-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .spotlight-content p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }


  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .stats-mini {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .spotlight {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .spotlight-image {
      order: -1;
    }
  }
</style>
